        "- ğŸ“¤ Upload `.py` files\n"
        "- â–¶ï¸ Run scripts\n"
        "- â¹ Stop scripts\n"
        "- ğŸ“„ View logs\n"
        "- ğŸ“ List your files\n"
        "- ğŸ›  Admin Panel (admin only)"
